好多爭執, 對上一個女朋友都係耶教徙<br />\n<br />\n唉, 好灰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就咪撚識耶閪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明, 但鐘意都無計架<br />\n<br />\n我都想佢唔係, 咁緣份都無法啦<br />\n<br />\n係我入左坑自己ON9"},{"pid":"583582693c5db086d6e9779c7cb6254cf3614c7a","tid":136812,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T11:06:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫佢睇多啲聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真 !我當初都係多睇聖經先會離教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a014a1dad002413f9c348c0b7abd9a0a23b4caa","tid":136812,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"點解要佢離教？<br />\n離咗教諗野多元化咗，<span style=\"color: green;\">隨時嫌你on99 </span>"},{"pid":"6779dd9ce90f3add29f5d6fdab943627ec8bdc03","tid":136812,"uid":45926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要佢離教？<br />\n離咗教諗野多元化咗，<span style=\"color: green;\">隨時嫌你on99 </span></blockquote><br />\n呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76da66a0993af823c4bde14d7fc24b19d44419a3","tid":136812,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T11:08:43.000Z","msg":"說服基督徒本人幾乎不可能，辯倒中間派先有啲可能"},{"pid":"96499f764a6f24dfa4c34b1624074d7c5905b489","tid":136812,"uid":24405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T11:08:54.000Z","msg":"講撚夠未呀屌你老母！"},{"pid":"ca9b827591bede19989a96ebc42d17ff5ca9b306","tid":136812,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係味想食人隻豬呀？</blockquote><br />\n唔係, 真心鐘意佢嘅<br />\n<br />\n不過佢係會十一奉獻個種, 對將來感到好大壓力<br />\n<br />\n亦都怕將來有好多爭執, 對上一個女朋友都係耶教徙<br />\n<br />\n唉, 好灰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就咪撚識耶閪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明, 但鐘意都