pid":"a68367eb5a1f9dd36680f451635e4994fb6831cb","tid":136812,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"果間野好邪，曾經去聽過<br />\n巴打千萬要小心"},{"pid":"9a6ac5e2fac6380bba46ce1d321aa80b80f0cf85","tid":136812,"uid":57723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:05:46.000Z","msg":"問佢耶穌如果係神 係無所不能<br />\n即係佢一早預見自己俾猶大出賣<br />\n點解要夾埋做場戲俾人類睇<br />\n等人類崇拜自己?<br />\n神係咪自戀狂?"},{"pid":"bd3b327053c67c2c5060cf23500a59f943b006ed","tid":136812,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:16:47.000Z","msg":"樓上好多巴打都叫樓主用理性方式質問<br />\n但實際上，中毒深既耶撚腦入面既理性已經被破壞得七七八八，要重新建立唔容易，我覺得最好用感性D既論點。要理解，一個人脫離宗教會失去左心靈支持，所以樓主要比多D關心你女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，當你既重要性大於教會，先有勝算。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://exchristian.hk/home/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fexchristian.hk%2Fhome%2F&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=acb883ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://exchristian.hk/home/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://truthbible.net/bloodybible/forchristians/#8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftruthbible.net%2Fbloodybible%2Fforchristians%2F%238&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ce790b2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://truthbible.net/bloodybible/forchristians/#8</a>"},{"pid":"63e03859a219ea57544fc1444446bb9213a65c3e","tid":136812,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:34:00.000Z","msg":"離教者之家有好多好文可以參考<br />\n樓主如果有D哲學底，理解一D形而上既觀點更加好，一個人就算無宗教，佢既超驗世界都唔會消失，只係換左個形式<br />\n你應該幫佢建立屬於佢自己個人既人生目標（唔係講小，耶撚係冇人生目標，佢地既人生得返教會）；等佢多D依靠你，多於依靠宗教，帶佢識多D非耶教朋友（<span style=\"color: green;\">當然要小心</span>）；理解下佢點解信，到底佢心理上缺乏左D咩；最後係適當時候加D理性比佢<br />\n<br />\n其實要幫人離教真係好難，連登如果有離教專家指教下就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64425c51f8192cd35fbbca10046229fb8b872f46","tid":136812,"uid":31704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:37:32.000Z","msg":"其實真係信神嘅存在個種人真係冇撚得講  問清楚個信教原因先好 一陣迫死人都唔知咩事 宗教自由如果佢冇迫你信由佢唔好咩"},{"pid":"41a75005c72187aa483e6e6268802b376285f287","tid":136812,"uid":51735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"不如我地開翻個離教討論 係telegram<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3b7c57b779127f5b62e2a55975166d2b20f0b0","tid":136812,"uid":40309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如我地開翻個離教討論 係telegram<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好阿, 我都想大家有個空間討論<br />\n傾下歷史, 宗教 異聞等都唔錯"},{"pid":"70e89291c979e74eeb015d628eb14d381a01b6b3","tid":136812,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:19:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係味想食人隻豬呀？</blockquote><br />\n唔係, 真心鐘意佢嘅<br />\n<br />\n不過佢係會十一奉獻個種, 對將來感到好大壓力<br />\n<br />\n亦都怕將來有好多爭執, 對上一個女朋友都係耶教徙<br />\n<br />\n唉, 好灰</blockquote><br />\n多鳩餘啦，之前有個女同事，竟然話朝頭早搭車返公司塞車係上帝嘅恩典，因為可以俾佢訓下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上撚晒腦</blockquote><br />\n我其實每朝都盼望港鐵壞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bc526a2cdd3807a01ca098b21a6800ee684bf5","tid":136812,"uid":51735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T17:12:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如我地開翻個離教討論 係telegram<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好阿, 我都想大家有個空間討論<br />\n傾下歷史, 宗教 異聞等都唔錯</blockquote><br />\n有冇人開 細佬比較少用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f231dcbcab063446fdf75e499cc0595848d2b0","tid":136812,"uid":70182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T19:34:27.000Z","msg":"信呢樣野係後情感合理化，<br />\n者係因為你女朋友信而令佢覺到教會咩都係正確。<br />\n<br />\n就好似你愛一個人，佢既缺點都會模糊化，<br />\n優點無限放大一樣。<br />\n<br />\n所以同佢講道理，佢會有1000萬個理由解釋你反基督。<br />\n<br />\n你要帶領佢自己體會基督教矛盾。<br />\n但唔可以從旁誘導，因為佢一建立左你反基督教形象，<br />\n你所有行為都變成有目的。<br />\n佢第一想法就係你搞事而唔係去了解自己被洗腦既問題。"},{"pid":"6954c0665456250a1991a666e145d7f5941f9251","tid":136812,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T19:46:30.000Z","msg":"係香港信天主教好過新教<br />\n<br />\n第時小朋友返學有好學校   死左又有墳場葬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n壓力大又可以去避靜   <br />\n<br />\n又唔會問你拎錢   教友網絡又大"},{"pid":"4594b6b95b98b06947ae458db0ccf5e7bd65f7c0","tid":136812,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T19:47:39.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係愛嘅就尊重人地個宗教信仰啦<br />\n廿幾歲人咁撚唔成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小心之心都要講句 睇死你都係想早啲食豬姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad01c7f527583e62d115122a0429cdaf1dc52215","tid":136812,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係愛嘅就尊重人地個宗教信仰啦<br />\n廿幾歲人咁撚唔成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小心之心都要講句 睇死你都係想早啲食豬姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邪教都要尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98eea4bc110fa638657d1b8e488b0723dab28b05","tid":136812,"uid":817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港信天主教好過新教<br />\n<br />\n第時小朋友返學有好學校   死左又有墳場葬<img s